	(1, 6, 'privacy-policy', 'Privacy Policy', '<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 17-01-2026</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Welcome to <strong>Medirilix</strong> (“we”, “our”, “us”).<br>We are committed to protecting your personal data and respecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, store, and protect your information when you use our website <strong>[website URL]</strong> or purchase products from us.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By accessing or using our website, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>1. About Us</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Website Name: <strong>[Your Website Name]</strong></li><li>Business Type: <strong>Single-Vendor E-commerce Platform</strong></li><li>Owner/Company Name: <strong>[Legal Business Name]</strong></li><li>Registered Address: <strong>[Business Address, India]</strong></li><li>Contact Email: <strong>[</strong><a href="mailto:support@yourdomain.com"><strong>support@yourdomain.com</strong></a><strong>]</strong></li><li>Contact Phone: <strong>[Phone Number]</strong></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We may collect the following types of personal data:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>a) Personal Information</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Full name</li><li>Email address</li><li>Mobile number</li><li>Billing and shipping address</li><li>Payment details (processed securely via third-party gateways)</li></ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>b) Account Information</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Username and password (encrypted)</li><li>Order history</li><li>Wishlist and preferences</li></ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>c) Technical &amp; Usage Data</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>IP address</li><li>Browser type and device information</li><li>Pages visited and time spent</li><li>Cookies and similar tracking technologies</li></ul>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We use your information to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Process and deliver orders</li><li>Manage payments and refunds</li><li>Communicate order updates and customer support</li><li>Improve website functionality and user experience</li><li>Prevent fraud and unauthorized transactions</li><li>Comply with legal and regulatory obligations</li></ul>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing (India – DPDP Act, 2023)</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We process your personal data based on:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Your <strong>consent</strong></li><li><strong>Performance of a contract</strong> (order fulfillment)</li><li><strong>Legal obligations</strong></li><li><strong>Legitimate business purposes</strong> permitted under Indian law</li></ul>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>5. Payment Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We <strong>do not store</strong> your debit/credit card or UPI details.<br>Payments are processed securely through trusted third-party payment gateways such as <strong>[Razorpay / PayPal / Others]</strong>, which follow PCI-DSS standards.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>6. Sharing of Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We may share your information only with:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Delivery and logistics partners</li><li>Payment gateway providers</li><li>IT and hosting service providers</li><li>Government or legal authorities when required by law</li></ul>\r\n\r\n<p>❌ We do <strong>not</strong> sell or rent your personal data to third parties.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>7. Cookies Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We use cookies to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Remember your preferences</li><li>Analyze website traffic</li><li>Improve performance and security</li></ul>\r\n\r\n<p>You can disable cookies through your browser settings, but some features may not work properly.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>8. Data Storage &amp; Security</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Data is stored on secure servers</li><li>Reasonable technical and organizational safeguards are implemented</li><li>Access to personal data is restricted to authorized personnel only</li></ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Despite our efforts, no system is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>9. Data Retention</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We retain personal data only for as long as:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Necessary to fulfill the purpose for which it was collected</li><li>Required by Indian laws (tax, accounting, legal compliance)</li></ul>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>10. Your Rights (As per Indian Law)</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>You have the right to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Access your personal data</li><li>Correct or update inaccurate data</li><li>Withdraw consent</li><li>Request deletion of your data (subject to legal obligations)</li><li>Grievance redressal</li></ul>\r\n\r\n<p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <strong>[support email]</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>11. Children’s Privacy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our website is <strong>not intended for children under 18 years</strong>.<br>We do not knowingly collect personal data from minors.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>12. Third-Party Links</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites.<br>We are not responsible for their privacy practices or content.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>13. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.<br>Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated “Last updated” date.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>14. Grievance Officer (India Compliance)</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As per Indian regulations, the Grievance Officer details are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Name: <strong>[Grievance Officer Name]</strong></li><li>Email: <strong>[</strong><a href="mailto:grievance@yourdomain.com"><strong>grievance@yourdomain.com</strong></a><strong>]</strong></li><li>Address: <strong>[Office Address]</strong></li><li>Response Time: Within <strong>7–15 working days</strong></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>15. Contact Us</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>📧 <strong>[</strong><a href="mailto:support@yourdomain.com"><strong>support@yourdomain.com</strong></a><strong>]</strong><br>📞 <strong>[Phone Number]</strong></p>', 1, NULL, 1, 1, '2026-01-17 08:20:17', '2026-01-17 08:25:51', NULL);
