	(1, 2, 'Medirilix', 'Trusted Partner in Medical Innovation', 'Medirilix', 'Welcome to Medirilix Enterprises your Trusted Partner in Medical Innovation Since 2023. Founded in 2023 and headquartered in New Delhi, India, Medirilix Enterprises is a dynamic sole proprietorship committed to advancing healthcare through innovation and quality.', '61zKrgYwgSuACwiFZdmL.png', 'RwCvrXowOJAev8SvZQSL.png', '1lPaSvzpUtXbuUocdFIm.png', 'Welcome to Medirilix Enterprises your Trusted Partner in Medical Innovation Since 2023. Founded in 2023 and headquartered in New Delhi, India, Medirilix Enterprises is a dynamic sole proprietorship committed to advancing healthcare through innovation and quality. We specialize in the manufacturing, export, and import of a comprehensive range of cutting-edge medical equipment and surgical instruments.', 'thThOj99KNHvQGR65b4S.png', 'All rights reserved', 'Maintained by Medirilix', '', NULL, 1, NULL, '2026-03-03 11:40:47', NULL);
